{"title":"Taquiarritmias-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Taquiarritmias-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"- Taquiarritmias","guid":"HFwOnAsgAre8T3WAXsNnKg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico de\\Ntaquicardia:","guid":"rCjsuQEjLwMIFyFDsAW2dg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. QRS estrecho\\N(<120 ms):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Ritmo irregular:","guid":"EG11cXukN5DNk38EbbmX3w","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"• Ondas P ausentes → ¿Ondas fibrilatorias? (Sí) → Fibrilación auricular (FA; Frecuencia Auricular (FA): 350-450 lpm)","guid":"ZRbTcXU0u26FoXt_WCqIug","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"• No → ≥ 3 morfologías diferentes de ondas P, PR variables → Taquicardia auricular multifocal (TAM)","guid":"u7RXuOg62EqBDiAqkqlTdg","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"• Ritmo regular:","guid":"dwmqtEwDbBKxTHdQtw1k0w","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• FA > frecuencia ventricular → Adenosina o maniobras vagales → Adenosina efectivo → AVNRT/AVRT","guid":"4Fti-ggNAhV0rmexydVWBg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• No efectivo → Taquicardia auricular focal (150-250 lpm)","guid":"ra3Zsii7eX6EF-CrkTvmpw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"2. QRS ancho\\N(≥120 ms):","guid":"lNTXUK8xHCsQ88mjAgXzQA","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• SVT con conducción aberrante:","guid":"FPnkVJTK8nF3lBftxpLJYg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Ritmo irregular:","guid":"y6XYkzZdrH-AyRvIgRAuOQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• FA con bloqueo de rama, Torsades de Pointes","guid":"VFWnK4pSXdwWvliH7Op56A","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"• Ritmo regular:","guid":"RK99HyU_B_lynpWZxHUiPQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• AVRT (antidrómica, preexcitación)","guid":"s_GzxYNySbduONGq8iIN8A","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• TV (Criterios de Brugada): Si → TV; No → Ritmo regular, podría ser TSV.","guid":"2Pqq4Nyl_f92rlC0PQxQGg","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación principal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"1. TSV:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• QRS estrecho (<120 ms)","guid":"lyWu0E1HmHY6A2ZtBBPmig","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Ritmo irregular → FA, TAM","guid":"EAYH2Di8Ylsl2nFbwLEtVw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• Ritmo regular → AVNRT, AVRT","guid":"yZxUk4VOwZZTYKPJI0dKQA","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"16","text":"2. Taquicardia ventricular (TV):","guid":"ULF970aPovkvd96XmV5cqQ","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• QRS ancho (≥120 ms)","guid":"ZR6Bj4T_8qGSCQnTSB5Xtg","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• Ritmo irregular/regular según presencia de criterios específicos.","guid":"SS-hNcVSoM5U1YZPriUWAw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":23,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Taquiarritmias-2024-1","id":"map_325","resolved_references":[]}